635653a0-7bc2-44f6-b43e-46a7770fc80b.title: Rock Stars of Connected Health Cybersecurity
635653a0-7bc2-44f6-b43e-46a7770fc80b.description: The 2016 must-attend cybersecurity event, Rock Stars of Connected Health Cybersecurity, brings together the 7 top C-level experts to talk about the newest and worst cyber threats. They’ll be telling you their strategies and solutions for preventing vulnerabilities

0e10664f-7da4-4746-8ed4-6d3e7a867d3e.title: Radiology Technical Exhibit
0e10664f-7da4-4746-8ed4-6d3e7a867d3e.description: Whereas current MRI systems are hazardous, noisy, claustrophobic, require specially shielded facilities, are expensive and complicated to purchase, install and operate, Bayes Imaging’s new compact MRI, in contrast, is safe, patient-and-operator-friendly, quiet, can be placed anywhere in a research or medical facility, inexpensive to purchase and install, cost-effective, and simple to operate and maintain.

info.title: The Mallinckrodt Institute of Radiology Annual Congress 2017
info.description: The goal of this conference is to enhance the health and well-being of members of the transgender community by (1) increasing the number of mental health and medical health care providers who feel comfortable and confident providing care for transgender patients; (2) increasing transgender community members’ knowledge, self-efficacy and advocacy skills through transgender centered educational sessions.

33d785d9-e9db-4406-a805-98f65364de27.name: Becton Dickinson
33d785d9-e9db-4406-a805-98f65364de27.description: For more than 114 years, BD has applied its technologies, resources, and institutional knowledge to help address fundamental health issues. The goal of BD's Global Health Initiative is to help strengthen healthcare systems and increase access to healthcare in the developing world.

35a38bfd-a35e-4ed1-89b4-182ddee88c55.name: Bayer
35a38bfd-a35e-4ed1-89b4-182ddee88c55.description: The NHS faces many challenges today around the increasing need for governance to demonstrate best patient care within increasing financial constraints. Bayer’s Radiology business is well placed to be the partner in helping trusts to address these challenges. With market-leading contrast media and power injector systems, Bayer is able to offer innovative patient care and with the addition of its informatics platform, it can support radiology departments in driving protocol standardisation and easily accessible audit data that enable departments to meet further challenges faced around contrast and radiation dose management.
